 4. Conditions of Distribution.

 4.1 License Text Requirement.

 When You Distribute the Work, Contributions, or Derivative Works,
 You must:

   (a) include a complete, unmodified copy of this License in a file
       named LICENSE (or COPYING) placed in the root directory or
       another prominent and accessible location; and

   (b) provide a URI or hyperlink to the canonical license text if
